<emphasis id="55CDEF554014466AFEA48665EB49B30E" box="[369,628,846,867]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="1264">Lepidactylus allardi</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="03284EB64014466AFD558665E876B3EF" author="Hancock ZB &amp; Wicksten MK" pageId="12" pageNumber="1264" pagination="101 - 127" refId="ref9462" refString="Hancock ZB, Wicksten MK. 2018. Two new species of sandburrowing amphipods of the genus Haustorius Muller, 1775 (Amphipoda: Haustoriidae) from the northwestern Gulf of Mexico. Zootaxa 4459: 101 - 127." type="journal article" year="2018">Hancock &amp; Wicksten, 2018</bibRefCitation>
